<h3>Our M&A Process</h3>
<ol class="process-timeline">
<li>
<h4>Initial Assessment</h4>
<p>Evaluate business value, market conditions, and transaction objectives</p>
</li>
<li>
<h4>Preparation</h4>
<p>Prepare financials, optimize operations, and develop transaction strategy</p>
</li>
<li>
<h4>Marketing</h4>
<p>Identify parties, create materials, and manage outreach process</p>
</li>
<li>
<h4>Negotiation</h4>
<p>Structure deal, negotiate terms, and maximize value</p>
</li>
<li>
<h4>Due Diligence</h4>
<p>Manage information exchange and address buyer/seller concerns</p>
</li>
<li>
<h4>Closing</h4>
<p>Finalize agreements, coordinate professionals, and close transaction</p>
</li>
</ol>

<h3>Transaction Types We Handle</h3>
<ul class="transaction-list">
<li><strong>Business Sales:</strong> Complete or partial sale of business to strategic or financial buyers</li>
<li><strong>Business Acquisitions:</strong> Strategic acquisitions and bolt-on purchases</li>
<li><strong>Mergers:</strong> Merger of equals and strategic combinations</li>
<li><strong>Management Buyouts:</strong> MBO structuring and advisory</li>
<li><strong>Partner Buyouts:</strong> Shareholder and partner transaction advisory</li>
<li><strong>Succession Planning:</strong> Family transfers and employee ownership transitions</li>
<li><strong>Distressed Sales:</strong> Expedited sales and distressed asset transactions</li>
</ul>

